{"tid":1747744,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實投完票既民調，個個答建制係會中伏？","createTime":"2019-11-23T11:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T11:20:43.000Z","uid":285794,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"628c7d28ebf9474b02206f885ce4f430e87f0cda","tid":1747744,"uid":285794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"突然諗起之前有幾日熱門post都話<br />\n票就投其他人<br />\n但係答就建制侯選人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗諗下如果我哋覺得佢哋一定種票/假票<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唯一反駁理據就係民調</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果民調出黎真係100%建制的話<br />\n反而顯示<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建制贏係正常</span></span>(佢可能種票/假票)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輸就唔正常</span></span>(佢真係光明正大咁選)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能有人話會令建制知道要吹雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得以現時社會狀況<br />\n佢有可能唔吹雞咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得坦白講自己投咗本土又好，泛民又好，甚至棄票(雖然我唔同意棄票)<br />\n好過出黎民調變咗<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">偏幫建制派</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同意既幫手推上熱門<br />\nP牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n曱近平<br />\n曱甴平"},{"pid":"249b604106ad7ceb769ca29a27a7922974237598","tid":1747744,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:01:21.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"60f1647170c02c715eb4aeaf9304ee78bc1167c7","tid":1747744,"uid":262428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"628c7d28ebf9474b02206f885ce4f430e87f0cda","tid":1747744,"uid":285794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0